Text: Yepppp. Started with a handful of chocolate chips. Pretty much ate an entire bag of chocolate chips :/

Author: -onebyonebyone-
Text: Oh noooooo. I do that every time I lose a few pounds.   I get overconfident and think, “hey I can treat myself to 1 Oreo,” even though I know damn well that my dumb ass is going to eat the entire sleeve in 2 minutes.
